//original definition in 1.2 of “category”: This provides information on the subject
            of what is being translated. For example: category="medical" for files from a medical
            related product. https://docs.oasis-open.org/xliff/v1.2/os/xliff-core.html#category

//In 1.2 “tool” was allowed in <file>, <phase>, <alt-trans>. Tool-id
            was allowed in <file>, <phase>, <alt-trans>, <tool>. Tool-name
            and tool-version were allowed in <tool>.
